 <section xml:id="sec-overview-rootfs">
 <title>Overview</title>
 <para>
 As &slema; was designed to use the read-only file system so after the deployment is complete, you are not able to perform direct modification to the root file system, e.g. by using <command>zypper</command>, the concept of transactional update has been implemented.
